<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 08:20:04 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>赫卡特与尼克斯艺术创作</title><link>https://some.pics/69dca72d13c13</link><description>&lt;p&gt;大约一年前，我完成了一个可爱的小艺术项目。

我从赫卡忒和原始女神尼克斯的象征意义中找到了许多心灵的慰藉。因此，我为她们创作了一幅艺术表现作品！ :)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Original artwork depicting the goddess Hecate with her snake, key, and dog, with the primordial goddess Nyx looking on from the night sky above." height="3300" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sjwallin/69dca72d13c13.jpg" width="2550"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sjwallin.some.pics"&gt;@sjwallin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 08:20:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>静止的自行车</title><link>https://some.pics/69dc39f9edf44</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🚲 静止的自行车&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A blue and green bike rests in a stand in grass along a portion of Montour Run." height="1815" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/brie/69dc39f9edf44.jpg" width="1815"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://brie.some.pics"&gt;@brie&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 00:34:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>今日天空</title><link>https://some.pics/69dc1baa72618</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今日天空&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Small patches of blue sky peak through a heavily clouded sky." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/69dc1baa72618.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 22:24:46 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>网关</title><link>https://some.pics/69dc004b99000</link><description>&lt;p&gt;网关。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A huge, closed door in a bright beige wall. And a concrete path leading there." height="4567" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69dc004b99000.jpg" width="2572"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 20:27:58 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>寿司表情</title><link>https: